text:
Starting from commit 357413 www/seamonkey doesn't install its desktop menu entry anymore.

I believe these removed lines in the Makefile are what is causing the issue:

- port-pre-install: 	 
- 	         ${ECHO_CMD} share/applications/${MOZILLA}.desktop >> ${PLIST} 	 
- 	         ${ECHO_CMD} 'share/pixmaps/${MOZILLA}.png' >> ${PLIST}


A seamonkey.desktop file is present in the work directory but not installed.
